section.draft-comment: This topic uses variables based on the bp_legal_vars.xml file. Update that file to modify output. Please do not change anything in this topic or rename the file. It is boilerplate and should have a 100% match with L10n translation memory. If you need to modify this topic, then it is no longer boilerplate and the translation memory is compared product version to version and not shared commonly across all products. If you change the file, please rename it too.
